  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The student is missing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A complaint has been lodged with Poovarasangulam police that a student named Rasendran Krupan (15 years old) studying at Sekkatipulavu School, Vavunia, has been missing since August 16.",
        "The brother of the missing student said that the said student got up from sleep at 1 am on the morning of the 16th and drank water and observed that he had been at home until then. When he woke up on the morning of the 16th at 4 am, the mother lodged a complaint at the Poovarasangulam Police Station that her son had gone missing.",
        "The student was reprimanded on the 15th for not going to class. It is suspected that the said student might have gone missing because of that. However",
        "The student's brother said that if anyone recognizes him, contact him on 0766922218, 0779987491."
      ],
